  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc6\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd -\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President should be given time to build the nation - Belbola Vipassi Nayake Thera",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The registrar of Kota Viharai Party, Japan's Prime Sanganayakar Venerable Belbola Vipassi Nayake Thera has said that the current President Ranil Wickremesinghe, who has a long political experience, should be given time to build the country.",
        "Thera pointed out that everyone should give up the system of ousting the rulers by conducting protests and cooperate with the President's plan to free the country from the current economic crisis and solve the problems of the people.",
        "Pointing out that the present President has fearlessly accepted the challenge while the country faces disaster, Thera expressed confidence that he will be able to overcome all challenges.",
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe, yesterday afternoon (24) went to Veheragoda Puradhana Viharai, Setavatta yesterday afternoon and while he was engaged in religious worship, the thera mentioned this while delivering a dedication speech.",
        "After visiting the vicar, the President worshiped Bodhi and engaged in religious activities, the Maha Sangha including Ambanwala Gnanaloka Thera of the Vicar President Sangha recited Prith and offered blessings to the President.",
        "After that, the President met the members of the Maha Sangha and inquired about their welfare.",
        "Historical Vihara Setavatta, Veharakoda Puradhana Viharai, Smt. Helena Wijewardena and Mr. It is a holy land given to Buddhism by Don Philip Wijewardana.",
        "Buddha Sasana Minister Vidura Wickramanayake, Member of Parliament Suren Raghavan and Executive Council President Amari Manthika Wijewardana and Secretary Channa Wickramasinghe were also present in the event."
      ],
